{"tha-ap141:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap141:0.2":"Sobhitavagga ","tha-ap141:0.3":"9 Salapupphadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap141:1.1":"“Migaraja tada asim, ","tha-ap141:1.2":"abhijato sukesari; ","tha-ap141:1.3":"Giriduggam gavesanto, ","tha-ap141:1.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap141:2.1":"Ayam nu kho mahaviro, ","tha-ap141:2.2":"nibbapeti mahajanam; ","tha-ap141:2.3":"Yannunaham upaseyyam, ","tha-ap141:2.4":"devadevam narasabham. ","tha-ap141:3.1":"Sakham salassa bhanjitva, ","tha-ap141:3.2":"sakosam pupphamaharim; ","tha-ap141:3.3":"Upagantvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap141:3.4":"adasim pupphamuttamam. ","tha-ap141:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap141:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap141:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap141:4.4":"pupphadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap141:5.1":"Ito ca navame kappe, ","tha-ap141:5.2":"virocanasanamaka; ","tha-ap141:5.3":"Tayo asimsu rajano, ","tha-ap141:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap141:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap141:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap141:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap141:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma salapupphadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap141:8.1":"Salapupphadayakattherassapadanam navamam. "}